{"tid":2095410,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《論香港革命之緣起》","createTime":"2020-07-05T12:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:39:17.000Z","uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"00f78638727bc5ea26f2f6bbdbf6a93b3fd04423","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"自回歸以降，香港已經埋下革命的種子。"},{"pid":"795ebb9d07a981350dd4bbb4fa295c99e0307e1d","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"大陸新移民之湧入"},{"pid":"b8acc02bc27cc8e0e5ebf06f0ea30d22c867d349","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"其後代為最激進的社會不穩定因素"},{"pid":"0e4eb802609afee8d79d9b15a542122e4baca4d3","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8acc02bc27cc8e0e5ebf06f0ea30d22c867d349","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"其後代為最激進的社會不穩定因素"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"大部分住公屋，亦有為數不少的住劏房。"},{"pid":"488812d323e178e20a72a7674ebd16ba3c5f43bb","tid":2095410,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWtmiWG.png&amp;h=a05a5c40&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"9df42878cc6e59a1aba18e4fb72565ab187463e6","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"新移民本身是文革的一代的後裔，新移民嫁了港人，便生下了八十至零零後。<br />\n<br />\n上世紀八十年代出世的人，大多擁有大專或以上的學歷，對中國文化理論上懷有恩情與敬意。但近代的中國文化是批鬥文化，乃文革之遺風。"},{"pid":"761760705b67a376ca0de3b219fe36cc918f71a4","tid":2095410,"uid":79893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"488812d323e178e20a72a7674ebd16ba3c5f43bb","tid":2095410,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWtmiWG.png&amp;h=a05a5c40&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"op係著名5毛"},{"pid":"b44cd9cd010318f3a18af8e01a54d28274fbbb45","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"中共官員曾經批評過，港獨分子在回歸前精蟲還未形成。而這些港獨分子，其母親是新移民佔大宗，還是老香港佔大宗呢？<br />\n<br />\n老香港，每當國家有難，不論天災還是人禍，都會義不容辭先捐錢救人。文革時寄物資、華東水災籌款捐錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cLnhqXhnDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2cLnhqXhnDA&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj30YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=113bb3e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cLnhqXhnDA</a>"},{"pid":"0d6c71cea87b782d7063f745371c2ce50113017f","tid":2095410,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"新移民及其後裔，他們會了解TBB《家變》入面鄧碧雲作為母親的角色嗎？還是懷有好勇鬥狠、崇尚武力之文革遺風？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理論上，紅衛兵的後裔便是香港革命的生力啤/新力軍。"}]}